<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby qd bḥtẖt ʿny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rabĩy qad̊
 baḥatẖ̊ta ʿanĩy fawajad̊tanī hunāk̊ fī
 halạk̊ fī ḍalạliⁿ wāb̊tiʿādiⁿ mitẖ̊lu ṭaẙriⁿ fī sẖirāk̊
 lạ ạảrāk̊ fakasar̊ta ạl̊fakẖã ḥālạaⁿ baʿ̊d̊ ạản̊ ạảd̊mat̊
 yadāk̊ man̊ siwāk̊ 2- ạảs̊maʿu ṣaẘta bukāʾiⁿ yaḥ̊milu ạlrĩyḥu ṣadāh
 mā turāh ại̹nã fī ạl̊bus̊tāni sẖakẖ̊ṣāaⁿ ạảẘhana ạl̊ḥuz̊nu
 qūāh wā̂dẖāh man̊ turāhu ại̹nãhu ạlrãbũ yasūʿu fī ṣalạẗ
 lilại̹lah 3- ại̹nãhu qad̊ dẖāba ḥuz̊nạaⁿ ại̹dẖ̊ rā̉y ạl̊maẘta
 ạl̊marīr̊ kam̊ ʿasīr̊</lyrics>
